 don't have nukes.   You don't want me to have nukes.  I'd nuke congress if I had nukes.  I'd shove the warhead right up Illhans vagina and run like hell.", "author": "5DchessWatch", "created": 1782846622765, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "BartzFFV", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "We're going to Nuke Mexico and it will be SCOTUS's fault", "last_comment_created": 1782847546231, "content": "<p>They backed us into a corner with the Birthright citizenship decision.</p>\n<p>This means we now have no choice but to address the root problem.  Or sterlize the rest of the world with biological agents.  We don't want to do the latter because of blowback which we've seen from covid.</p>\n<p>SO</p>\n<p>We have to FIX OTHER COUNTRIES' CRIME</p>\n<p>(THEN OUR OWN)</p>\n<p>They don't solve it themselves.  So we'll solve it for them.</p>\n<p>We're going to nuke the cartels</p>\n<p>And then during cleanup, we'll torture the remaining to tell us who in the FBI and CIA and Congress and SCOTUS and other agencies they're working with.</p>\n<p>By <em>We</em> I mean Trump.</p>\n<p>I'm not going to do it.  I don't have nukes.   You don't want me to have nukes.  I'd nuke congress if I had nukes.  I'd shove the warhead right up Illhans vagina and run like hell.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 30, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "\ud83d\udca9\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0SHITPOST\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\ud83d\udca9", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_com